WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.480
In Atlanta's heart, Community Movement

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:05.585
Builders (CMB) emerges as a 
beacon of hope and action.

00:00:05.585 --> 00:00:09.560
A Black member-based 
collective, CMB serves the working-class

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:15.976
and poor Black communities, united in the face of 
gentrification, displacement, and over-policing.

00:00:15.976 --> 00:00:16.476
Their mission to empower black communities

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:24.326
challenging existing institutions and 
creating new ones under their control.

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:28.600
Through community organizing 
and cooperative economics, CMB is building

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:32.722
a future where Black communities 
thrive with autonomy and justice.

00:00:32.830 --> 00:00:37.353
Join Community Movement Builders in 
their pursuit to bring power back to the people.

00:00:39.134 --> 00:00:43.424
Stand with us. 
Empower. Organize. Transform.
